@startuml
title UC: Add/Remove Camera to Favorites (Logged-in User)

actor "User" as U
boundary "Favorites UI" as FUI
control "FavoritesController" as FC
entity "FavoriteList" as FL
entity "Camera" as C

U -> FUI: Click ⭐ Add to Favorites
FUI -> FC: addFavorite(userId, cameraId)

FC -> FL: loadOrCreate(userId)
FL --> FC: favoriteListId

FC -> C: findById(cameraId)
C --> FC: camera

FC -> FL: addCamera(camera)
FL --> FC: added

FC --> FUI: Update favorites panel (added)
FUI --> U: Camera appears in favorites

@enduml